  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n77/mode/1up">74</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n78/mode/1up">75</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. mēl oṭuveṉap peyar koṭuttōtiya vēṟṟumaiccol mūṉṟāvatām. atu viṉaimutaluṅ karuviyumākiya iraṇṭumutalaiyum poruḷākavuṭaittu e-ṟu.</p>
<p>mēl aiyoṭu kuvveṉṟōtiyavaḻi āṉurupuntaḻuvappaṭṭamaiyāṉ, īṇṭum avvāṟē koḷḷappaṭum; paṭavē, mūṉṟāvatātalum viṉaimutal karuvipporuṭṭātalum āṉurupiṟkumeytum.</p>
<p>viṉaimutalāvatu karuvi mutalāyiṉa kāraṇaṅkaḷait toḻiṟpaṭuttuvatu. karuviyāvatu viṉaimutaṟṟoḻiṟpayaṉaic ceyappaṭuporuṭkaṇuyppatu.</p>
<p>aṉaiyeṉpatu attaṉmaiyavākiya mutaleṉa avaṟṟatilakkaṇattiṟkut tōṟṟuvāy ceytavāṟu.</p>
<p>mutaleṉpataṟku mēlēyuraittām.</p>
<p>u - m. koṭiyoṭu tuvakkuṇṭāṉ; ūciyoṭu kuyiṉṟa tūcum paṭṭum. e - m. akattiyaṉāṟṟamiḻuraikkappaṭṭatu; vēlāṉeṟintāṉ. e-m. varum.</p>
<p>piṟaporuḷumuḷavēṉum viṉaimutal karuvi ciṟantamaiyāṉ, viṉaimutalkaruviyaṉaimutaṟṟeṉṟār.</p>
<p>viṉaimutalkaruvikkaṇ oṭuveṉurupu ikkālattarukiyallatu vārātu.	(12)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
